AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/Thu%E1%BA%ADn-ngh%E1%BB%8Bch-h%E1%BB%93i-v%C4%83n-thi/poem-TmrQmiCwY3CAdTG93vUvUA">Thuận nghịch hồi văn thi - 順逆迴文詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Th%C6%B0-t%E1%BA%B7ng-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-huynh-ph%C3%B3-thu-th%C3%AD/poem-0gyyjoiroExY7cErvoBNYQ">Thư tặng đường huynh phó thu thí - 書贈堂兄赴秋試</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Nguy%C3%AAn-H%C3%A0nh/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Th%E1%BB%A9/poem-eJL278Fml-ezEMjLR883dw">Tống Đường Thứ - 送唐次</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Nguy%C3%AAn-H%C3%A0nh/author-xb9f8XgZhtsCrJqig5eRWg">Vũ Nguyên Hành</a>)<br></div>	</div>
